test_all_one_range:
assert [] == [1, 1, 1, 1]
  Right contains 4 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1, 1, 1]
  + []
test_odd_same_number:
assert [] == [-11, -11, -11, -11]
  Right contains 4 more items, first extra item: -11
  Full diff:
  - [-11, -11, -11, -11]
  + []
test_even_range:
assert [2, 4, 6] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: 2
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [2, 4, 6]
